Tiring Critical										CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat.Critical				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Critical Focus																								PREMULT:1,[PRETOTALAB:13],[PREVARGTEQ:CriticalFocusQualify,13]																																																																											DESC:Your critical hits cause opponents to become fatigued.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.135																																																																					BENEFIT:Whenever you score a critical hit, your opponent becomes fatigued. This feat has no additional effect on a fatigued or exhausted creature.
