Arcane Talent											CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																																																																	PRERACE:1,RACESUBTYPE=Elf,RACESUBTYPE=Gnome																							PRESTAT:1,CHA=10																																																																			DESC:Magic is in your blood, and at your fingertips.																																																																									BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Arcane Talent Selection|1																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.151																																																															BENEFIT:Choose a 0-level spell from the sorcerer/wizard spell list. You can cast this spell three times per day as a spell-like ability. The caster level is equal to your character level. The save DC is %1|CHA+10
