Ectoplasmic Spell											CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Metamagic																																																																																																																																																																				DESC:Your spells breach the gulf between dimensions, sending ghostly emanations into the ether.																																																															ADDSPELLLEVEL:1																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.158																																																															BENEFIT:An ectoplasmic spell has full effect against incorporeal or ethereal creatures. An ectoplasmic spell uses up a spell slot one level higher than the spell's actual level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													FACT:AppliedName|Ectoplasmic
