Shared Insight											CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																																																																	PRERACE:1,Half-Elf																											PRESTAT:1,WIS=13																																																																			DESC:You deftly direct others' attentions where you wish.																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.169																																																															BENEFIT:As a move action, you can grant all friendly creatures within 30 feet who can see or hear you a +2 bonus on Perception checks for a number of rounds equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1 round).
