Coordinated Charge					CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat.Teamwork							PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,TYPE=Teamwork																																																																																																																																																																																							PRETOTALAB:10																																												DESC:You are an expert at leading your allies into the fray.																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.93															BENEFIT:When an ally with this feat charges a creature that is no further away from you than your speed, you can, as an immediate action, charge that creature. You must be able to follow all of the normal charge rules.
