Improved Two-Weapon Feint				CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat									PREABILITY:4,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Expertise,Improved Two-Weapon Fighting,Two-Weapon Fighting,Two-Weapon Feint																																												PREMULT:1,[PRESTAT:1,INT=13],[PREVARGTEQ:CombatFeatIntRequirement,13]	PREMULT:1,[PREVARGTEQ:PreStatScore_DEX,17],[PREVARGTEQ:FeatDexRequirement,17]																																																																																																							PRETOTALAB:6																																												DESC:Your primary weapon keeps a foe off balance, allowing you to slip your off-hand weapon past his defenses.																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.106															BENEFIT:While using Two-Weapon Fighting to make melee attacks, you can forgo your first primary-hand melee attack to make a Bluff check to feint an opponent. If you successfully feint, that opponent is denied his Dexterity bonus to AC until the end of your turn.
