Shaitan Style						CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat.Style								PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Elemental Fist,Improved Unarmed Strike																																																				PREMULT:1,[PRETOTALAB:9],[PREVARGTEQ:MonkFeatQualify,5]																																																																																																			PRESTAT:2,CON=13,WIS=15																																																														DESC:You strike with the caustic forces from within the earth.																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.118															BENEFIT:You gain one additional Elemental Fist (Advanced Player's Guide 158) attempt per day. While using the Shaitan Style and Elemental Fist feats to deal acid damage, you gain a bonus on acid damage rolls equal to your Wisdom bonus. Further, if your Elemental Fist melee attack misses while you are using it to deal acid damage, you still deal 1d6 points of acid damage to your target.
