Siege Gunner						CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat									PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Siege Engineer																																																																																																																																	PRESKILL:1,Profession (siege engineer)=5																																																																																														DESC:Aiming outsized siege weapons poses little difficulty for you.																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.118															BENEFIT:You take no size penalty for aiming a directfire siege weapon larger than yourself. If you operate an indirect-fire siege weapon and miss, you misdirect fire by 1 square per range increment. &nl; [Normal] Direct-fire weapons impose a -2 attack roll penalty per size category by which the weapon is larger than the creature aiming it. An indirect-fire weapon that misses misdirects fire by 1d4 squares per range increment.
